{"id":966566175,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"2 weeks, 6 days","timestamp":1686222459,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"5 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/966566175/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Two Sum IV - Input is a BST","memory":"44.9 MB","code":"/**\n * Definition for a binary tree node.\n * public class TreeNode {\n *     int val;\n *     TreeNode left;\n *     TreeNode right;\n *     TreeNode() {}\n *     TreeNode(int val) { this.val = val; }\n *     TreeNode(int val, TreeNode left, TreeNode right) {\n *         this.val = val;\n *         this.left = left;\n *         this.right = right;\n *     }\n * }\n */\nclass Solution {\n    boolean ans=false;\n    public boolean findTarget(TreeNode root, int k) {\n        HashSet<Integer> hm= new HashSet<>();\n        help(root,k,hm);\n        return ans;\n        \n    }\n    public void help(TreeNode root,int k,HashSet<Integer> hm){\n        if(root==null){\n            return;\n        }\n        if(hm.contains(root.val)){\n            ans=true;\n        }\n        else{\n           hm.add(k-root.val);\n        }\n        help(root.left,k,hm);\n        help(root.right,k,hm);\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"two-sum-iv-input-is-a-bst","has_notes":false}
